name: Mirajane embedding
description:
This is an embedding to invoke Mirajane Strauss from Fairy Tail in your prompts.

How to use it ? Simply put the file in the 'embeddings' folder and add 'abcdef_mirajane' to your prompt tags.

It's my first embedding, and even if I like the final result with the right parameters, there is some troubles sometime; here few suggestions to avoid them :

  • Use a good mixed model to avoid blurry results (mine is OrangeCocoa 50/50 Mix from Corneo).

  • Always start with a lot of quality tags (like 'masterpiece, best quality, hyper detailed, highres, official art, 8k, (realistic:1.1)').

  • There still sometimes a crossing out on the picture, especialy on eyes; or a watermark.

If you follow these steps you should get the same quality results as mine.

Good generations !
